document_data.caption: A map showing Elyssyrr in southern Gwynneth.
document_data.name: Elyssyrr
document_data.mainbody: '''Elyssyrr''' was a small coastal town located on the island of [[Gwynneth]] within the [[Moonshae Isles]].{{Cite interactive atlas}}{{Cite dungeon/196/Backdrop: The Moonshae Isles}}
document_data.Geography: Elyssyrr was found in southern Gwynneth in the western region of the kingdom of [[Corwell]]. The town was located along the northern shore of [[Corwell Firth]] just south of [[the Highlands]] within [[the Shrouded Lands]].
